title: Madden NFL 16 Roster Update For Week 5 of the NFL Season Available Now
text: Madden NFL 16 Roster Update For Week 5 of the NFL Season Available Now 04:32 PM - October 8, 2015 by Steve_OS Week 5 of the NFL season is here and so are the updated Madden NFL 16 rosters. Check out the blog here , along with the sortable spreadsheet of all changes here . Of note, Von Miller joins Marshal Yanda, Aaron Rodgers, J.J. Watt and Rob Gronkowski as the only players in the game with an overall 99 rating. GOING UP A.J. Green, Cincinnati Bengals WR (+1 OVR to 94) Kam Chancellor, Seattle Seahawks SS (+1 OVR to 95) Devonta Freeman, Atlanta Falcons HB (+3 OVR to 81) Tavon Austin, St. Louis Rams WR (+2 OVR to 78) Ryan Delaire, Carolina Panthers DE (+5 OVR to 66) Todd Gurley, St. Louis Rams RB (+1 OVR to 80) Cameron Heyward, Pittsburgh Steelers LE (+2 OVR to 90) Aldon Smith, Oakland Raiders LE (+1 OVR to 92) Calais Campbell, Arizona Cardinals LE (+1 OVR to 97) Charles Woodson, Oakland Raiders SS (+1 OVR to 89) GOING DOWN Robert Mathis, Indianapolis Colts ROLB (-1 OVR to 84) Odell Beckham Jr., New York Giants WR (-1 OVR to 93) Travis Kelce, Kansas City TE (-1 OVR to 91) Aqib Talib, Denver Broncos CB (-1 OVR to 91) Dwayne Bowe, Cleveland Browns WR (-2 OVR to 81) Frank Gore, Indianapolis Colts RB (-2 OVR to 81) Alfred Morris, Washington Redskins RB (-1 OVR to 85) Andre Johnson, Indianapolis Colts WR (-1 OVR to 84)
